				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Watching their video and reading their full feature list is an eye-opening (and gut-wrenching) experience! The demo link and purchasing page gives it reality which your summary can't fully convey. Saying it can decode CAPTCHA isn't as powerful as seeing the most convoluted images get decoded.
